headline: Nilesh Shah joins Illumina as Head of Region, AMEA
summary: Illumina Inc. (NASDAQ: ILMN), a global leader in DNA sequencing and array-based technologies, announced today the appointment of Nilesh Shah as Head of Region, AMEA, effective immediately.
